phenomenon through exploratory research and, when higher reliability is needed,
confirmatory research. The workstream keeps PR/FAQ, explanation candidates,
exploratory / diagnostic notes, reviewed pre-registrations for planning and
reporting discipline, and an IMRAD-shaped manuscript draft.

